<br>
Otherwise, I don't PP.  You have to be relatively close to the mob, and I don't like being that close.  Give me max melee distance over an ability I feel vaguely guilty about any day. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustrykninedshiv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stryknine DShiv</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/10/02 9:54:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Personally-</span><hr size=1> There are only 10 hotkeys on my &quot;combat&quot; hotkey page. Every one is used, and there isn't any room for something like &quot;pick pocket&quot;.  I got my skill to 200 by practicing on a boat or other PCs , and very rarely used it when fighting. <br>
<br>
